Dialogue: 1,0:18:44.11,0:18:48.64,ed-cn-2,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(300,300)}缓缓深吸一口气
Dialogue: 1,0:18:48.64,0:18:53.14,ed-cn-2,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(300,0)}宴会就此拉开帷幕
